{"tha-ap94:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap94:0.2":"Sudhavagga ","tha-ap94:0.3":"2 Sucintikattheraapadana ","tha-ap94:1.1":"“Tissassa lokanathassa, ","tha-ap94:1.2":"suddhapithamadasaham; ","tha-ap94:1.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap94:1.4":"buddhassadiccabandhuno. ","tha-ap94:2.1":"Attharase ito kappe, ","tha-ap94:2.2":"raja asim maharuci; ","tha-ap94:2.3":"Bhogo ca vipulo asi, ","tha-ap94:2.4":"sayananca anappakam. ","tha-ap94:3.1":"Pitham buddhassa datvana, ","tha-ap94:3.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","tha-ap94:3.3":"Anubhomi sakam kammam, ","tha-ap94:3.4":"pubbe sukatamattano. ","tha-ap94:4.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap94:4.2":"yam pithamadadim tada; ","tha-ap94:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap94:4.4":"pithadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap94:5.1":"Atthatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap94:5.2":"tayo te cakkavattino; ","tha-ap94:5.3":"Ruci uparuci ceva, ","tha-ap94:5.4":"maharuci tatiyako. ","tha-ap94:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap94:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap94:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap94:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sucintiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap94:8.1":"Sucintikattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}